  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/94a06a9a5298176dcf11dda6500ca0d3.poster.avif?t=1756725619\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/94a06a9a5298176dcf11dda6500ca0d3.webm?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/94a06a9a5298176dcf11dda6500ca0d3.mp4?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're at the top! Money no longer excites you. In the seek for a greater thrill, you join a new casino with a far greater stake than money... <strong>Your Life</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your friends to a game of chance in this 2-4 Player Online Experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/416900f60c6e45c3a3a7556369a98ebf.poster.avif?t=1756725619\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/416900f60c6e45c3a3a7556369a98ebf.webm?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/416900f60c6e45c3a3a7556369a98ebf.mp4?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/42adbf4f0aa2ae4de3c995710ff67861.poster.avif?t=1756725619\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/42adbf4f0aa2ae4de3c995710ff67861.webm?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/42adbf4f0aa2ae4de3c995710ff67861.mp4?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cannons are pointed at you and your friends. Decide a target, then spin the wheel to decide their fate. If you target yourself and no bullet is fired, you get to take another turn. Take out your opponents by reducing their health to zero. <strong>Become the last person standing.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/1342a5c2153daa3cd2503b1754ada864.poster.avif?t=1756725619\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/1342a5c2153daa3cd2503b1754ada864.webm?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/1342a5c2153daa3cd2503b1754ada864.mp4?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/0d678129c3ccadda294272ebae058ba9.poster.avif?t=1756725619\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/0d678129c3ccadda294272ebae058ba9.webm?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/0d678129c3ccadda294272ebae058ba9.mp4?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you don't have to rely solely on luck. Use consumable items to tip the odds in your favor. The central roulette wheel determines the effectiveness of your item. If you take the risk and bet on green, the effects of your items are greatly enhanced. The effects of your items can range from reversing the turn order, to blocking a player's turn, to dealing double damage, among many other powerful abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/f575f6eb2f50f085d96ad6214783e4fb.poster.avif?t=1756725619\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/f575f6eb2f50f085d96ad6214783e4fb.webm?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954260/extras/f575f6eb2f50f085d96ad6214783e4fb.mp4?t=1756725619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
